<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/noi-that-tron-goi-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"noi-that-tron-goi\" class=\"wp-image-9759\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/noi-that-tron-goi-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/noi-that-tron-goi-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/noi-that-tron-goi-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/noi-that-tron-goi-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/noi-that-tron-goi-2048x1536.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/noi-that-tron-goi.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh thi c\u00f4ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia th\u00e0nh t\u1eebng c\u00f4ng \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00e1c nhau v\u1edbi tr\u00ecnh t\u1ef1 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, tr\u00e1nh ch\u1ed3ng ch\u00e9o c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c gi\u00fap ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian. Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia l\u00e0m hai c\u00f4ng \u0111o\u1ea1n ch\u00ednh bao g\u1ed3m: thi c\u00f4ng ph\u1ea7n th\u00f4 v\u00e0 thi c\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thi c\u00f4ng th\u00f4 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng gian. C\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7n x\u1eed l\u00fd trong c\u00f4ng \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y g\u1ed3m x\u1eed l\u00fd tr\u1ea7n, s\u00e0n, chia kh\u00f4ng gian, ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i\u1ec7n, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean l\u1ea1c, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng th\u00f4ng kh\u00ed, \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a,&#8230; Vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e2n chia kh\u00f4ng gian c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7n ph\u00e1 b\u1ecf v\u00e1ch t\u01b0\u1eddng ho\u1eb7c x\u00e2y l\u00ean m\u1ed9t v\u00e1ch t\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1c, do \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh to\u00e1n quy tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ed3ng ch\u00e9o, c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf nhau.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thi c\u00f4ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n sau khi ph\u1ea7n th\u00f4 v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t xong. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t. Sau khi l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 b\u1ea3n v\u1ebd \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t tr\u1ecdn g\u00f3i ph\u1ea3i v\u1ec7 sinh c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd r\u1ed3i b\u00e0n giao cho gia ch\u1ee7.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/Phong-khach-5-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"noi-that-tron-goi\" class=\"wp-image-9763\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/Phong-khach-5-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/Phong-khach-5-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/Phong-khach-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/Phong-khach-5-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/Phong-khach-5-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/Phong-khach-5-scaled.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1edbi N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Byzan, m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ho\u00e0n m\u1ef9 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o 3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1: c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ti\u1ec7n nghi, t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 cao, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ea1t chu\u1ea9n. Do \u0111\u00f3, d\u00f9 \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u00f4ng \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0o ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e2m huy\u1ebft v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung cao \u0111\u1ed9. Kh\u00f4ng d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o tr\u00ec s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n 10 nam nh\u1eb1m h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>L\u1ee3i \u00edch khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t tr\u1ecdn g\u00f3i<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u1edf tr\u00ean, c\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t tr\u1ecdn g\u00f3i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn, x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c kh\u00e2u t\u1eeb A &#8211; Z trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t. Sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch m\u00e0 gia ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thi c\u00f4ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t tr\u1ecdn g\u00f3i:&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>\u0110\u1ed3ng nh\u1ea5t trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c<\/li><li>Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed<\/li><li>D\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t<\/li><li>\u0110\u00fang y\u00eau c\u1ea7u mong mu\u1ed1n<\/li><li>Th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gu th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 ri\u00eang<\/li><li>H\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o tr\u00ec d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/4.2-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"thiet-ke-thi-cong-noi-that-tron-goi\" class=\"wp-image-9760\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/4.2-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/4.2-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/4.2-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/4.2-450x253.jpg 450w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/4.2-140x79.jpg 140w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/4.2.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Byzan&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Byzan &#8211; Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u s\u1ed1 1 phong c\u00e1ch Hi\u1ec7n \u0110\u1ea1i. H\u01a1n 10 n\u0103m 1 phong c\u00e1ch, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 mang t\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ngh\u00ecn gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t tr\u1ecdn g\u00f3i s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o cho c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0, nh\u00e0 ph\u1ed1, bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1, villa. Hi\u1ec7n nay, n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Byzan \u0111ang cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t tr\u1ecdn g\u00f3i t\u1eeb A &#8211; Z g\u1ed3m:&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t&nbsp;<\/li><li>S\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t<\/li><li>Thi c\u00f4ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t&nbsp;<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"512\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/1-1024x512.jpg\" alt=\"thiet-ke-thi-cong-noi-that-tron-goi\" class=\"wp-i